library(readr)
library(dplyr)
ds_salaries <- read_csv("/Users/zoezurasky/Desktop/MGSC310/datasets/ds_salaries.csv")
ds_salaries_clean <- ds_salaries %>%
    select(-salary, -salary_currency, -employee_residence, -remote_ratio,
        -company_location, -company_size, -work_year)
library(rsample)
ds_salary_split <- initial_split(ds_salaries_clean, prop = 0.75)
ds_salary_train <- training(ds_salary_split)
ds_salary_test <- testing(ds_salary_split)
